122
00:11:39,366 --> 00:11:41,201
- Tiada sesiapa akan tahu.
- Terima kasih.

123
00:12:02,013 --> 00:12:03,098
Maaf kami terlambat.

124
00:12:06,017 --> 00:12:07,644
- Kenapa lambat?
- Bukan urusan mak.

125
00:12:07,686 --> 00:12:09,354
Saya benci kejutan. Apa yang berlaku?

126
00:12:09,979 --> 00:12:11,648
Tom. Gembira bertemu awak.

127
00:12:12,148 --> 00:12:15,151
Melanie, seronok dapat jumpa awak.

128
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,821
Selalu yang paling cantik.

129
00:12:17,904 --> 00:12:19,614
Saya dengar komen baik
tentang rekaan awak.

130
00:12:19,656 --> 00:12:21,908
Oh, ya. Terima kasih.

131
00:12:28,748 --> 00:12:33,753
Andrew. Melanie memakai cincin
di jari yang paling penting.

132
