171
00:16:17,394 --> 00:16:19,104
- Senyap, Bear!
- Senyap, Bryant!

172
00:16:23,775 --> 00:16:25,068
Apa jadi dengan Bear?

173
00:16:26,778 --> 00:16:29,155
Dia dah mati. Awak tiada di sini.

174
00:16:31,241 --> 00:16:32,659
